    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[AddedById], [p].[CustomerId], [p].[CustomerStatusId], [p].[DateAdded], [p].[DateModified], [p].[IsWithdrawal], [p].[ModifiedById], [p].[PortfolioId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[AddedById] AS [AddedById0], [c].[BirthDate], [c].[CustomerNumber], [c].[CustomerTypeId], [c].[CountryId], [c].[DateAdded] AS [DateAdded0], [c].[DateModified] AS [DateModified0], [c].[FirstName], [c].[GenderId], [c].[IdDocumentTypeId], [c].[IdNumber], [c].[LastName], [c].[MaritalStatusId], [c].[MiddleName], [c].[ModifiedById] AS [ModifiedById0], [c].[OccupationId], [c].[Phone], [c].[TitleId], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[AddedBy], [p0].[DateAdded] AS [DateAdded1], [p0].[DateModified] AS [DateModified1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[IsScheme], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[Name]
    FROM [PortfolioCustomer] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Customer] AS [c] ON [p].[CustomerId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Portfolio] AS [p0] ON [p].[PortfolioId] = [p0].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [t].[Id0] = [a].[CustomerId]
LEFT JOIN [CustomerCarrier] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id0] = [c0].[CustomerId]
LEFT JOIN [EmailAddress] AS [e] ON [t].[Id0] = [e].[CustomerId]
LEFT JOIN [MobileNumber] AS [m] ON [t].[Id0] = [m].[CustomerId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[AddedBy], [t].[DateAdded], [t].[DateModified], [t].[Description], [t].[IsScheme], [t].[ModifiedBy], [t].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[AddedById], [p0].[CustomerId], [p0].[CustomerStatusId], [p0].[DateAdded], [p0].[DateModified], [p0].[IsWithdrawal], [p0].[ModifiedById], [p0].[PortfolioId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[AddedBy], [p].[DateAdded], [p].[DateModified], [p].[Description], [p].[IsScheme], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[Name]
    FROM [Portfolio] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [PortfolioCustomer] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[PortfolioId]

INNER JOIN [MotorMake] AS [m0] ON [m].[MotorMakeId] = [m0].[Id]
